= Introduction =

xmonad-config is the Xmonad and xmobar configuration used by Vic Fryzel.
http://github.com/vicfryzel/xmonad-config


= Requirements =

== Haskell Packages ==
 * xmonad 0.9.1
 * xmonad-contrib 0.9.1
 * xmobar 0.11.1


= Installation =

$ cd
$ mv .xmonad .xmonad.orig
$ git clone git@github.com:vicfryzel/xmonad-config.git .xmonad


= Notes =

The key bindings are listed in xmonad.hs.

The colors set in the xmobar config are meant to coincide with the IR_Black
terminal and vim themes found at http://blog.infinitered.com/entries/show/6.
